  "detailed_description": "《You, Calligrapher》is an authentic VR Calligraphy simulator.<br><br>In《You, Calligrapher》, you will be empowered to imitate the masterpieces of poets and scholars, draw and paint with traditional ink pen. Experience the culture of Calligraphy with your own hands!<br><br>The game is  100% compatible with <strong>Oculus Quest</strong> and <strong>Rift</strong>, please use airlink or alvr to connect.<br>And also compatible with <strong>Valve Index</strong>, <strong>HTC</strong> and <strong>WMR</strong> devices.<br><br>Find us in Discord:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/b72f4f082a09173608747f943d2b13f6.poster.avif?t=1697601243\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/b72f4f082a09173608747f943d2b13f6.webm?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/b72f4f082a09173608747f943d2b13f6.mp4?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Realistic ink brush physics<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/11546637838391b40b433b798c1f863f.poster.avif?t=1697601243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/11546637838391b40b433b798c1f863f.webm?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/11546637838391b40b433b798c1f863f.mp4?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Mutiple mixable Colours<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/e8efdd1d6f4cedc8d764d69d64ae2fcb.poster.avif?t=1697601243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/e8efdd1d6f4cedc8d764d69d64ae2fcb.webm?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/e8efdd1d6f4cedc8d764d69d64ae2fcb.mp4?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Caligraphy and Chinese learning<br><br>- Templates of masterpieces<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/325f93d5760e87c734eec17bc1793977.poster.avif?t=1697601243\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/325f93d5760e87c734eec17bc1793977.webm?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/325f93d5760e87c734eec17bc1793977.mp4?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Save & Share your words, paints, illustrations...etc<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/20ceb407c16973d1d0580570ee06ad93.poster.avif?t=1697601243\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/20ceb407c16973d1d0580570ee06ad93.webm?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593700/extras/20ceb407c16973d1d0580570ee06ad93.mp4?t=1697601243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
